{"id":3015,"date":"2022-12-22T17:50:42","date_gmt":"2022-12-22T16:50:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/?page_id=3015"},"modified":"2023-01-27T12:18:22","modified_gmt":"2023-01-27T11:18:22","slug":"info-for-presenters-panellists-workshop-leaders","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/info-for-presenters-panellists-workshop-leaders\/","title":{"rendered":"Info for Presenters, Panellists &#038; Workshop Leaders"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1024x576.png\" alt=\"Improving Discovery and Collaboration in Open Science\" class=\"wp-image-2812\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1536x864.png 1536w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Dear Panelists, Presenters and Workshop leaders,&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We look forward to welcoming you to our final TRIPLE conference, \u201cImproving Discovery and Collaboration in Open Science\u201d, in Bonn\u00a0 (Germany) from the 1st to the 3rd of February. This page provides general information to plan your stay in Bonn, Germany and lists the information the organisational team needs in preparation for the event.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Information for you:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Please <strong>register <\/strong>via this link: <a href=\"https:\/\/triple2023.sciencesconf.org\/registration\">https:\/\/triple2023.sciencesconf.org\/registration<\/a>. Please keep in mind: If you have already registered to submit an abstract, you are <strong>not automatically registered <\/strong>as a participant in the conference.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Find <strong>travel info<\/strong> and info on the <strong>conference venue<\/strong> \u201cWissenschaftszentrum\u201d here: <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/events\/travel-information\/\">https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/events\/travel-information\/<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Please note that the final TRIPLE conference is planned as a <strong>hybrid event<\/strong>. Presenters and Panelists will be recorded. Please fill out the <strong>license agreement<\/strong> you can find here: <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/License-Agreement.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/License-Agreement.pdf\">License Agreement<\/a>.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>From January on you will find a preliminary programme here: <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/the-conference-program\/\">https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/the-conference-program\/<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Information we need from you:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>If you have yet to do so, please provide us with a\u00a0<strong>picture\u00a0<\/strong>(300dpi)and\u00a0<strong>your short biography<\/strong>\u00a0(100 words max.). If you are organizing a\u00a0<strong>panel\/workshop<\/strong>, please give a brief abstract for your workshop (250 words max.) Also, please provide us with\u00a0<strong>short biographies of your panellists\/workshop leaders.\u00a0<\/strong>All this information must be submitted to the administrative team by the 5th of January via your account on sciencesconf.org.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Please send us your <strong>presentation <\/strong>by the 25th of January.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any further questions or issues, do not hesitate to contact the administrative team and email our communication officer Sona Arasteh (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"mailto:arasteh@maxweberstiftung.de\" target=\"_blank\">arasteh@maxweberstiftung.de<\/a>).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With kind regards,&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your TRIPLE Team<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Dear Panelists, Presenters and Workshop leaders,&nbsp; We look forward to welcoming you to our final TRIPLE conference, \u201cImproving Discovery and Collaboration in Open Science\u201d, in Bonn\u00a0 (Germany) from the 1st to the 3rd of February. This page provides general information<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13,"featured_media":2812,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3015"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/13"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3015"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3015\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3200,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3015\/revisions\/3200"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2812"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3015"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}